{"tid":364438,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A] Mitrasphere (6) 肝到2046","createTime":"2017-08-18T11:23:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-18T11:31:03.000Z","uid":16666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3cbce41fccfc78f7cfb3ead5efed65bcdfca6e52","tid":364438,"uid":16666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T11:23:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">14號下午2點開始每日一次一石10連 7日共送70連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">新手唔好怕麻煩 唔該睇睇#2 #3</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://gamewith.akamaized.net/service/hd/images/426689515fe6db51c8d8b1b6a93852f7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgamewith.akamaized.net%2Fservice%2Fhd%2Fimages%2F426689515fe6db51c8d8b1b6a93852f7.png&h=5e3c4d07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日文名: ミトラスフィア<br />\n<br />\n大量聲優坐陣<br />\n<img src=\"https://gamewith.akamaized.net/img/b20dead2abeac8b7dd7487aa5999fbc4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgamewith.akamaized.net%2Fimg%2Fb20dead2abeac8b7dd7487aa5999fbc4.jpg&h=ff6d3acd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://gamewith.akamaized.net/service/hd/images/4c781f37bd665ef36feacb7b7fd3b832.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgamewith.akamaized.net%2Fservice%2Fhd%2Fimages%2F4c781f37bd665ef36feacb7b7fd3b832.jpg&h=11350770&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男女聲優合共20幾位慢慢J<br />\n連龍珠婆婆都有參與其中<br />\n<br />\n回合制, 自定造型, 每職業8種武器 加 5防具<br />\n<img src=\"https://gamewith.akamaized.net/img/8b1740b6bd26cdd0769a2c24c3c1e9c3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgamewith.akamaized.net%2Fimg%2F8b1740b6bd26cdd0769a2c24c3c1e9c3.jpg&h=e904e804&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大量動作同叫聲可以係地圖亂用<br />\n<img src=\"https://gamewith.akamaized.net/img/b28cc26b52bfa05445393dd236e7a016.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgamewith.akamaized.net%2Fimg%2Fb28cc26b52bfa05445393dd236e7a016.jpg&h=48b3197e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5種職業<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.img-conv.gamerch.com/img.gamerch.com/mitrasphere/1486109666.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.img-conv.gamerch.com%2Fimg.gamerch.com%2Fmitrasphere%2F1486109666.jpg&h=ec9f4a14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劍術士: 單體物理最強<br />\n護術士: 坦得落BUFF又可自己補自己<br />\n聖導士: 補師冇咩好講啦, 最緊要有得蘇生<br />\n弓術士: 群攻技, 支援, 大大力BUFF<br />\n魔導士: 大大力魔師, 群技<br />\n<br />\n介紹片:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WYsjX75WHAQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWYsjX75WHAQ&d=zAT6WAKOHv6hVv7mK2DwF7DFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=b5a0e903\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WYsjX75WHAQ</a>"},{"pid":"76a07e88a2f0255d1f08620f8c6b80bf68b669e6","tid":364438,"uid":82068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T11:25:10.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"450646bf9678093408587352af5537815390fa41","tid":364438,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T11:26:52.000Z","msg":"應該7先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"426c8412d107e6ec4d1529d520e4936aa2060871","tid":364438,"uid":1731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T11:27:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該7先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗緊有咩地方怪怪地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db15fa0461d3c636b9c626c407dcbeac7dce4cbf","tid":364438,"uid":16666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T11:29:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Q&amp;A</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>Q:首抽抽咩好, 點抽好?</strong></span><br />\n<strong>A:</strong> 評價網 - <br />\n<a href=\"https://altema.jp/mitrasphere/bukilist?rea%5B%5D=4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faltema.jp%2Fmitrasphere%2Fbukilist%3Frea%255B%255D%3D4&d=zAT6WAKOHv6hVv7mK2DwF7DFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=e2ff4eee\" target=\"_blank\">https://altema.jp/mitrasphere/bukilist?rea%5B%5D=4</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://altema.jp/mitrasphere/risemara\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faltema.jp%2Fmitrasphere%2Frisemara&d=zAT6WAKOHv6hVv7mK2DwF7DFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=f3bdb2b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://altema.jp/mitrasphere/risemara</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">8月14號開始, 一開波送石夠你70連 <strong>(4星機率 10%) 暫時4星最頂, 冇5星</strong></span><br />\n<br />\nStep1 -\t免費10連, 魔具嚟, 咩職都用得 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.altema.jp/mitrasphere/buki/ico/237.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.altema.jp%2Fmitrasphere%2Fbuki%2Fico%2F237.jpg&h=e84d64f3&s={SIZE}\" />劍/魔最好有呢舊野 <span style=\"color: red;\">下一擊100%爆擊</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.altema.jp/mitrasphere/buki/ico/249.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.altema.jp%2Fmitrasphere%2Fbuki%2Fico%2F249.jpg&h=99a61b08&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://img.altema.jp/mitrasphere/buki/ico/213.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.altema.jp%2Fmitrasphere%2Fbuki%2Fico%2F213.jpg&h=42f1428f&s={SIZE}\" />坦就呢舊 群體吸仇恨 / 回血<br />\n<br />\nStep2 -\t250石10連保底1件4*武: (同光武POOL一樣,但光POOL冇保底) <br />\n\t抽全職武器果個POOL, 如果玩死一職, 最好一下就抽中自己職煌武<br />\n<br />\nStep3 -\t250石10連保底1件4*武:<br />\n\t當你抽完全職POOL, 抽到你想要嘅武, 就ALL IN職業限定POOL 到你抽到理想為止<br />\n<br />\nStep4 - 水pool 每日1石10連<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>or</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n唔好煩 All in 自己職, 一樣有機會出煌武, 靚就開, 唔識就睇#3, 覺得自己好蠢 睇極都唔識先問人啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>Q: 又係ON9要突武game, 玩嚟做乜?</strong></span><br />\n<strong>A:</strong> 每把武可以突5次, 4星食2,3(20%)星都得, 絕對唔似其他game 咁on9要焗你食相同星<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>Q: 有冇PVP 同公會?</strong></span><br />\n<strong>A:</strong> 冇, 共鬥為主, 可以開房組隊一齊打任, 或者抱課長大腿farm裝過關<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>Q: 除左抽仲點拎其他裝?</strong></span><br />\n<strong>A:</strong> 打主線, 活動, 會送4星勁裝 (現時建議谷戰力打活動狼王, 獎品豐富, 包括4星防具 突滿會係現時最強防具 - 數值偏向物魔防, 想魔攻高不適用)<br />\n遲下仲有更多時裝活動, 大量時裝俾你改造型<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>Q: 武器係咪要升技嫁?</strong></span><br />\n<strong>A:</strong> 要, 但唔洗抽相同武, 可以分解冇用武黎升技 <br />\nPS: 抽到最勁果把野記得放第一個武器位, 因為主線會有得免費升技1次<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>Q: 一開波係劍士, 係咪可以轉職?</strong></span><br />\n<strong>A:</strong> 可以隨時轉, 想玩咩就玩咩, 唔洗升技升能力<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>Q: 造型係咪SET死?</strong></span><br />\n<strong>A:</strong> 唔係, 可以隨時更改配搭, 幫囡囡換衫<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>Q: 一開GAME要揀男女同改名, 之後有冇得改先?</strong></span><br />\n<strong>A:</strong> 可以, 男女24小時換1次<br />\n名可以重用,但要改就要課金石(100)先改到<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>Q: 造型好似唔係幾夠洗喎?</strong></span><br />\n<strong>A:</strong> 唔止, 隻game有探索功能, 每1個鐘探1次, 最多儲5次, 執地圖閃閃下嘅(可以用石加上限或回滿)<br />\n探索可以拎到唔同嘅珍珠去換石,強化資源,勁裝,同埋頭髮造型<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/GwoW7i1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FGwoW7i1.jpg&h=481ca144&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上圖為取自kekeke某位人兄嘅探索結果, 魔具能力 - 魔攻特大UP<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/15/082432_6f46a20848275838b51556edfb8f4ae4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F15%2F082432_6f46a20848275838b51556edfb8f4ae4.jpg&h=4874e803&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>Q: 講左咁耐, 點引繼呀?</strong></span><br />\n<strong>A:</strong> 請注意 ios同an 互轉可能會冇晒免費石 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/07/204940_c1292010a4198004614c9b19589715d1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F07%2F204940_c1292010a4198004614c9b19589715d1.jpg&h=e9930cfa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/07/204941_5e056194f3ceec2dda3575e5b3af3271.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F07%2F204941_5e056194f3ceec2dda3575e5b3af3271.jpg&h=d67bbd6b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/07/204942_1679be55d6c27697ed124180294ce673.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F07%2F204942_1679be55d6c27697ed124180294ce673.jpg&h=c3509645&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖片由 darksze巴打提供<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>Q: 強化關點入呀??</strong></span><br />\n<strong>A:</strong>強化關卡時間表 <span style=\"color: red;\">紅豆 - 武器專用</span><br />\n每場最高22xx粒豆 打足一粒鐘約10幾萬<br />\n（）外時間是日本時間，（）內時間是台灣/香港時間<br />\n請注意必須要轉日本時間<br />\n請注意必須要轉日本時間<br />\n請注意必須要轉日本時間<br />\n所以說3次<br />\n<br />\n時段以下：<br />\n<br />\n第一段時間08：00am(07:00am)<br />\n第二段時間12:00am(11:00pm)<br />\n第三段時間20:00pm(07:00pm)<br />\n第四段時間22:00pm(10:00pm）<br />\n<br />\n如果沒轉日本時間遊戲內08:00am,12:00am,20:00pm,22:00pm不會有強化關卡出現，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">藍豆 - 防具專用</span><br />\n曜日上級每場約1000粒左右<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">綠豆 - 裝飾專用</span><br />\n故事地圖 見到有共闘100%就入去打, 付場每人送你100粒豆, 共400左右<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>Q: 有冇3星勁防具?</strong></span><br />\n<strong>A:<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/15/082430_7d75fb5c936486ad6ba1020e12696221.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F15%2F082430_7d75fb5c936486ad6ba1020e12696221.jpg&h=b58ba401&s={SIZE}\" /></strong>"},{"pid":"a85e1cf8b48296d98f59727ad0831f147fd9d38f","tid":364438,"uid":16666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T11:29:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>應該7先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗緊有咩地方怪怪地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br /